Hi Dave,

I have Vanagon seats in my 73/74/79 Westfakia,they fit perfectly into the
tracks on the 1979 seat pedestals.

However, they are taller than the stock 74 seat, placing you about 3/4"
closer to the roof.


Happy trails,

Greg Potts
1973/74/79 Westfakia Conversion  **Bob the Tomato **
